CPK
***

    This document describes CPK, a program written by Eric G. Suchanek,
Ph.D. The program has been designed to allow the user to quickly and
easily display space-filling molecular models on the Amiga personal
computer. The program also interfaces to the popular public domain ray
tracer `POV-Ray', See @{"POV-Ray" Link "POV-Ray"}, for more information.


